snippet.title: SILICON SCRAMBLE v1.10 ~ 504,938,800
snippet.description:
Self-destruct your way to victory in SILICON SCRAMBLE, a 3 minute caravan shmup!

This game was originally made in one week for the Gunner Parade '22 game jam, winning 1st place overall!

Play for free on itch.io: https://crows-nest.itch.io/silicon-scramble
